### Get token from Keycloak (requires Direct Access Grants enabled on patient-frontend client)
# @name login
POST http://localhost:8080/realms/patientmanagement/protocol/openid-connect/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=password&client_id=patient-frontend&username=testuser@test.com&password=password123

###

@token = {{login.response.body.access_token}}

### Get All Patients (uses token from above)
GET http://localhost:4004/api/patients
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
